           go to     prn-fin-lr1-700.
       prn-fin-lr1-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento preliminare, in area di comodo,    *
      *              * degli importi relativi al conteggio provvi-     *
      *              * gionale                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-gpc-tip-ctg       to   w-ass-ctg-tip-ctg      .
           move      rf-gpc-ibl-pvg       to   w-ass-ctg-ibl-pvg      .
           move      rf-gpc-amm-pvg       to   w-ass-ctg-amm-pvg      .
           move      rf-gpc-imp-doc       to   w-ass-ctg-imp-doc      .
           move      rf-gpc-imp-agf       to   w-ass-ctg-imp-agf      .
           perform   ass-age-ctg-000      thru ass-age-ctg-999        .
       prn-fin-lr1-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento il numero di documenti trattati per  *
