      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-liv-age-num-dft      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento totale imponibile provvigionale per  *
      *              * l'agente a credito o a debito                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ass-ctg-ibl-pvg    >    zero
                     add   w-ass-ctg-ibl-pvg
                                          to   w-liv-age-tot-icr
           else      add   w-ass-ctg-ibl-pvg
                                          to   w-liv-age-tot-idb      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento totale ammontare provvigioni per     *
      *              * l'agente a credito o a debito                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ass-ctg-amm-pvg    >    zero
                     add   w-ass-ctg-amm-pvg
                                          to   w-liv-age-tot-pcr
           else      add   w-ass-ctg-amm-pvg
                                          to   w-liv-age-tot-pdb      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento totale imponibile provvigionale per  *
      *              * l'agente                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       w-ass-ctg-ibl-pvg    to   w-liv-age-tot-ibl      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento totale ammontare provvigioni per     *
      *              * l'agente                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       w-ass-ctg-amm-pvg    to   w-liv-age-tot-pvg      .
       prn-fin-lr1-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se non e' prevista stampa : ad eventuale ag-    *
      *              * giornamento del flag di elaborazione per agenti *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-age-300-sns       not  = "S" and
                     rr-age-300-sns       not  = "T"
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-700.
       prn-fin-lr1-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa del conteggio provvigionale              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   stp-ctg-pvg-000      thru stp-ctg-pvg-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se flag di interruzione forzata: uscita         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-999.
       prn-fin-lr1-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Update del record testata fattura con il flag   *
      *              * di elaborazione per agenti                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       prn-fin-lr1-710.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se si e' in simulazione non si esegue co-   *
      *                  * munque l'update                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tip-exe           =    01
                     go to prn-fin-lr1-730.
       prn-fin-lr1-720.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Update                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione parametri                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   l-age-300-tip-ope      .
           move      rf-fit-num-prt       to   l-age-300-prt-fit      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Richiamo modulo                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "pgm/age/prg/obj/page3005"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-age-300              .
       prn-fin-lr1-730.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Continuazione                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-fin-lr1-900.
       prn-fin-lr1-900.
