           perform   sel-rec-fir-000      thru sel-rec-fir-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se selezione fallita : ad uscita            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fir-sel-flg-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-liv-det-900.
       prn-liv-det-260.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
