      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione della % di sconto effettiva                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-psc-eff-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione preliminare                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-psc-eff-cln      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-psc-eff-cnn      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-psc-eff-dpf      .
       det-psc-eff-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione della percentuale di sconto per  *
      *              * confronto tra prezzo lordo standard e netto di  *
      *              * vendita                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se lordo standard a zero : no calcolo       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-pls    =    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se netto di vendita a zero : no calcolo     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-pnv    =    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione della differenza prezzo      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-det-psc-eff-pnv    from w-det-psc-eff-pls
                                        giving w-det-psc-eff-dpf      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se la differenza prezzo e' minore o uguale  *
      *                  * a zero : no calcolo                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-dpf    >    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-200
           else      go to det-psc-eff-300.
       det-psc-eff-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se differenza prezzo per sconto         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione della percentuale u- *
      *                          * nica di sconto                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-psc-eff-pls    to   w-det-pme-sop-ibl      .
           move      w-det-psc-eff-dpf    to   w-det-pme-sop-amm      .
           perform   det-pme-sop-000      thru det-pme-sop-999        .
           move      w-det-pme-sop-per    to   w-det-psc-eff-cln      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * A trattamento altro tipo sconto     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     det-psc-eff-300.
       det-psc-eff-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione della percentuale di sconto per  *
      *              * confronto tra prezzo netto standard e netto di  *
      *              * vendita                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se netto standard a zero : no calcolo       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-pns    =    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se netto di vendiata a zero : no calcolo    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-pnv    =    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione della differenza prezzo      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-det-psc-eff-pnv    from w-det-psc-eff-pns
                                        giving w-det-psc-eff-dpf      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se la differenza prezzo e' minore o uguale  *
      *                  * a zero : no calcolo                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-psc-eff-dpf    >    zero
                     go to det-psc-eff-400
           else      go to det-psc-eff-500.
       det-psc-eff-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se differenza prezzo per sconto         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione della percentuale u- *
      *                          * nica di sconto                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-psc-eff-pns    to   w-det-pme-sop-ibl      .
           move      w-det-psc-eff-dpf    to   w-det-pme-sop-amm      .
           perform   det-pme-sop-000      thru det-pme-sop-999        .
           move      w-det-pme-sop-per    to   w-det-psc-eff-cnn      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * A trattamento altro tipo sconto     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     det-psc-eff-500.
       det-psc-eff-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * La % di sconto unica proveniente dall'accorpa-  *
      *              * mento tra le 5 % sconto in riga, viene calcola- *
      *              * ta altrove                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       det-psc-eff-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-psc-eff-999.
       det-psc-eff-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione della % di provvigione a fronte di un im-  *
      *    * porto provvigionale a forfait                             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-det-per-aff-ibl = Imponibile provvigionale     *
      *    *          w-det-per-aff-pvg = Importo provvigione a for-   *
      *    *                              fait                         *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-det-per-aff-per = Percentuale determinata      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Note   : La percentuale determinata viene posta a zero, e *
      *    *          in questo caso vengono posti pure a zero l'impo- *
      *    *          nibile passato e l'importo passato, nei seguenti *
      *    *          casi                                             *
      *    *            - Imponibile passato pari a zero               *
      *    *            - Importo a forfait passato pari a zero        *
      *    *            - % determinata a zero in quanto insignifican- *
      *    *              te                                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          Nel caso in cui l'importo a forfait passato, in  *
      *    *          base all'imponibile passato, dovesse determina-  *
      *    *          re una % uguale o superiore al 100%, la percen-  *
      *    *          tuale viene ridotta al 99%, e viene ricalcolato  *
      *    *          l'importo forfettario.                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-per-aff-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se imponibile a zero : uscita con zero          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-per-aff-ibl    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-pvg
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-per
                     go to det-per-aff-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se importo a forfait a zero : uscita con zero   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-per-aff-pvg    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-pvg
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-per
                     go to det-per-aff-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Calcolo della percentuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-per-aff-pvg    to   w-det-per-aff-w01      .
           multiply  100                  by   w-det-per-aff-w01      .
           divide    w-det-per-aff-ibl    into w-det-per-aff-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-aff-per
                                                         rounded      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se % determinata a zero : uscita con zero       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-per-aff-per    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-pvg
                     move  zero           to   w-det-per-aff-per
                     go to det-per-aff-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se % determinata inferiore a 100 : uscita       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-per-aff-per    <    100,0
                     go to det-per-aff-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Forzatura della % al 99%                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      99,0                 to   w-det-per-aff-per      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ricalcolo dell'importo forfettario              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-per-aff-ibl    to   w-det-per-aff-pvg      .
           multiply  w-det-per-aff-per    by   w-det-per-aff-pvg      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-aff-pvg      .
       det-per-aff-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione dell'ammontare provvigione a fronte di un  *
      *    * imponibile provvigionale e di 3 perecentuali              *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-det-amm-pvg-ibl     = Imponibile provvigionale *
      *    *          w-det-amm-pvg-per (1) = 1.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-amm-pvg-per (2) = 2.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-amm-pvg-per (3) = 3.a percentuale          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-det-amm-pvg-pvg     = Ammontare provvigioni    *
      *    *                                  determinato              *
      *    *          w-det-amm-pvg-per (1) = Percentuale unica rical- *
      *    *                                  colata                   *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Note   : Se non si ricava alcun ammontare tutti i valori  *
      *    *          vengono posti a zero                             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-amm-pvg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se imponibile a zero : uscita con zero          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-amm-pvg-ibl    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg
                     go to det-amm-pvg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se percentuali tutte a zero : uscita con zero   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                                          =    zero and
                     w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                                          =    zero and
                     w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                                          =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg
                     go to det-amm-pvg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riduzione delle tre percentuali ad una singola  *
      *              * percentuale                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-amm-pvg-w01      .
           move      100                  to   w-det-amm-pvg-w02      .
      *
           move      w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                                          to   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           multiply  w-det-amm-pvg-w02    by   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-amm-pvg-w03
                                                         rounded      .
           add       w-det-amm-pvg-w03    to   w-det-amm-pvg-w01      .
           subtract  w-det-amm-pvg-w03    from w-det-amm-pvg-w02      .
      *
           move      w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                                          to   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           multiply  w-det-amm-pvg-w02    by   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-amm-pvg-w03
                                                         rounded      .
           add       w-det-amm-pvg-w03    to   w-det-amm-pvg-w01      .
           subtract  w-det-amm-pvg-w03    from w-det-amm-pvg-w02      .
      *
           move      w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                                          to   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           multiply  w-det-amm-pvg-w02    by   w-det-amm-pvg-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-amm-pvg-w03
                                                         rounded      .
           add       w-det-amm-pvg-w03    to   w-det-amm-pvg-w01      .
           subtract  w-det-amm-pvg-w03    from w-det-amm-pvg-w02      .
      *
           move      w-det-amm-pvg-w01    to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)  .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)  .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se l'unica percentuale e' a zero : uscita con   *
      *              * zero                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                                          =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg
                     go to det-amm-pvg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Calcolo dell'ammontare provvigione              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-amm-pvg-ibl    to   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg      .
           multiply  w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                                          by   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-amm-pvg-pvg
                                                         rounded      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se l'ammontare provvigione e' a zero : uscita   *
      *              * con zero                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-amm-pvg-pvg    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-ibl
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)
                     move  zero           to   w-det-amm-pvg-pvg
                     go to det-amm-pvg-999.
       det-amm-pvg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione della % media di provvigione in base a :   *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * - Imponibile provvigionale                                *
      *    * - Importo    provvigione                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * N.B.: attualmente il campo che ospita la % e' di 2 carat- *
      *    *       teri e quindi non puo' superare il 99,9%            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-pme-sop-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione preliminare %                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-pme-sop-per      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se imponibile a zero : uscita con zero          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-pme-sop-ibl    =    zero
                     go to det-pme-sop-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se importo provvigione a zero : uscita con zero *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-pme-sop-amm    =    zero
                     go to det-pme-sop-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se importo provvigione maggiore dell' imponibi- *
      *              * le : uscita con zero                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-pme-sop-amm    >    w-det-pme-sop-ibl
                     go to det-pme-sop-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Calcolo della percentuale                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           multiply  100                  by   w-det-pme-sop-amm      .
           divide    w-det-pme-sop-ibl    into w-det-pme-sop-amm
                                        giving w-det-pme-sop-per
                                                         rounded      .
       det-pme-sop-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione % unica da max 5 % distinte                *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-det-per-uni-001     = 1.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-per-uni-002     = 2.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-per-uni-003     = 3.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-per-uni-004     = 4.a percentuale          *
      *    *          w-det-per-uni-005     = 5.a percentuale          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-det-per-uni-per     = Unica percentuale        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-per-uni-000.
           move      100                  to   w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           multiply  w-det-per-uni-001    by   w-det-per-uni-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           subtract  w-det-per-uni-w03    from w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           add       w-det-per-uni-w03    to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           multiply  w-det-per-uni-002    by   w-det-per-uni-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           subtract  w-det-per-uni-w03    from w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           add       w-det-per-uni-w03    to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           multiply  w-det-per-uni-003    by   w-det-per-uni-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           subtract  w-det-per-uni-w03    from w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           add       w-det-per-uni-w03    to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           multiply  w-det-per-uni-004    by   w-det-per-uni-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           subtract  w-det-per-uni-w03    from w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           add       w-det-per-uni-w03    to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           multiply  w-det-per-uni-005    by   w-det-per-uni-w01
                                        giving w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-per-uni-w03      .
           subtract  w-det-per-uni-w03    from w-det-per-uni-w01      .
           add       w-det-per-uni-w03    to   w-det-per-uni-w02      .
      *
           move      w-det-per-uni-w02    to   w-det-per-uni-per      .
       det-per-uni-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione di un importo scontato                     *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-det-imp-sco-iml         = Importo lordo        *
      *    *          w-det-imp-sco-psc(01..05) = % di sconto          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-det-imp-sco-imn         = Importo netto        *
      *    *          w-det-imp-sco-ams         = Ammontare sconto     *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-imp-sco-000.
           move      w-det-imp-sco-iml    to   w-det-imp-sco-imn      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-imp-sco-inx      .
       det-imp-sco-100.
           add       1                    to   w-det-imp-sco-inx      .
           if        w-det-imp-sco-inx    >    5
                     go to det-imp-sco-900.
           if        w-det-imp-sco-psc
                    (w-det-imp-sco-inx)   =    zero
                     go to det-imp-sco-100.
           subtract  w-det-imp-sco-psc
                    (w-det-imp-sco-inx)   from 100,0
                                        giving w-det-imp-sco-w01      .
           multiply  w-det-imp-sco-imn    by   w-det-imp-sco-w01
                                        giving w-det-imp-sco-w02      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-imp-sco-w02
                                        giving w-det-imp-sco-imn
                                                         rounded      .
           go to     det-imp-sco-100.
       det-imp-sco-900.
           subtract  w-det-imp-sco-imn    from w-det-imp-sco-iml
                                        giving w-det-imp-sco-ams      .
       det-imp-sco-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione totali documento                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : rf-fit-iva-cst    = Castelletto Iva in record    *
      *    *                              [fit]                        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-det-tot-doc-tot = Totale documento             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-det-tot-doc-ibl = Totale imponibile            *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-det-tot-doc-iva = Totale Iva                   *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-tot-doc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totale documento                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-iva-tdo       to   w-det-tot-doc-tot      .
       det-tot-doc-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totali imponibile e imposta, per sommatoria dei *
      *              * valori contenuti nel castelletto Iva            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       det-tot-doc-210.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione preliminare totali          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-tot-doc-ibl      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-tot-doc-iva      .
       det-tot-doc-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Inizializzazione indice 1..6                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-tot-doc-ctr      .
       det-tot-doc-230.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento indice 1..6                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-det-tot-doc-ctr      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine ciclo : ad uscita                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-tot-doc-ctr    >    6
                     go to det-tot-doc-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice Iva a zero : si ignora l'elemento *
      *                  * in esame                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-fit-iva-cod
                    (w-det-tot-doc-ctr)   =    zero
                     go to det-tot-doc-230.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sommatoria imponibile                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       rf-fit-iva-ibl
                    (w-det-tot-doc-ctr)   to   w-det-tot-doc-ibl      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sommatoria imposta                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       rf-fit-iva-imp
                    (w-det-tot-doc-ctr)   to   w-det-tot-doc-iva      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo su elemento successivo              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-tot-doc-230.
       det-tot-doc-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-tot-doc-999.
       det-tot-doc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Descrizione in lingua per la stampa di : spese per la     *
      *    * fatturazione e sconti in chiusura e pagamento             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-des-zsf-000.
