           move      spaces               to   w-det-tmo-fat-tmo      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su protocollo                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-tmo-fat-prt    =    zero
                     go to det-tmo-fat-900.
       det-tmo-fat-100.
