           if        w-rlt-sts            not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-pvg-cor-aaa-800.
       det-pvg-cor-aaa-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione record [fir]                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rlt-rec-dat-fir      to   rf-fir                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione area w-fir                         *
