      *                  *                riga                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fir-vlb-imp-rig    to   w-det-amm-pvg-ibl      .
           move      rf-fir-ppv-rig (1)   to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (1)  .
           move      rf-fir-ppv-rig (2)   to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (2)  .
           move      rf-fir-ppv-rig (3)   to   w-det-amm-pvg-per (3)  .
           perform   det-amm-pvg-000      thru det-amm-pvg-999        .
       det-pvg-cor-aaa-320.
