      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-fir-prz-prz-lrs    to   w-det-pme-sop-ibl      .
           move      w-det-abt-rig-dpf    to   w-det-pme-sop-amm      .
           multiply  -1                   by   w-det-pme-sop-amm      .
           perform   det-pme-sop-000      thru det-pme-sop-999        .
           move      w-det-pme-sop-per    to   w-det-abt-rig-pum      .
