      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-abr-mau-mag    =    100
                     go to det-abt-rig-640
           else if   w-prs-abr-mau-mag    >    100 and
                     w-prs-abr-mau-mag    <    200
                     go to det-abt-rig-660
           else      go to det-abt-rig-680.
