           move      w-det-abt-rig-pum    to   w-det-abt-rig-psa      .
           multiply  w-det-abt-rig-pda    by   w-det-abt-rig-psa      .
           divide    100                  into w-det-abt-rig-psa      .
           add       w-det-psr-per-pvg    to   w-det-abt-rig-psa      .
