      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fir-mag-tip-rig    not  = "A"
                     go to stp-ctg-pvg-atr-600.
           move      05                   to   w-stp-srr-ctr-inx      .
           move      "Righe che non contribuiscono alla provvigione     
      -              ""                   to   w-stp-srr-tot-pmt
                                              (w-stp-srr-ctr-inx)     .
           move      w-fir-vlb-imp-rig    to   w-stp-srr-cmd-nte      .
           perform   stp-ctg-pvg-atx-000  thru stp-ctg-pvg-atx-999    .
       stp-ctg-pvg-atr-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totale 06 : righe di acconto o addebito         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       stp-ctg-pvg-atr-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
