      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-fir-ocl-dat       =    w-rrf-ocl-dat and
                     rf-fir-ocl-num       =    w-rrf-ocl-num
                     go to stp-ctg-pvg-eco-900.
       stp-ctg-pvg-eco-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
