           move      "VP"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      25                   to   p-lin                  .
           add       w-dsp-dsp-vrt        to   p-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-ctg-pvg-eco-430.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
